---
import NeonBackground from './NeonBackground.astro';
import Animations from './Animations.astro';
import NeonEffects from './NeonEffects.astro';
---

<section class="faq py-20 text-white relative overflow-hidden" id="faq">
  <NeonBackground />
  <Animations />
  <NeonEffects />

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 z-10 relative">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-green-400 animate-pulse-slow">
      Preguntas Frecuentes
    </h2>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6" id="accordion-flush" data-accordion="collapse">
      <!-- Pregunta 1 -->
      <div class="border border-purple-500/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-purple-400 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in-up">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">
          <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300" data-accordion-target="#faq-body-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-body-1">
            <span>¿Qué procesos puedo automatizar con IA?</span>
            <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </h3>
        <div id="faq-body-1" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="faq-heading-1">
          <div class="p-5 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Puedes automatizar chatbots, flujos de trabajo, análisis de datos y más, ahorrando tiempo y mejorando la eficiencia.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Pregunta 2 -->
      <div class="border border-green-500/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-green-400 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">
          <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 text-green-400 hover:text-green-300" data-accordion-target="#faq-body-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-body-2">
            <span>¿Cómo manejan mis redes sociales?</span>
            <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </h3>
        <div id="faq-body-2" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="faq-heading-2">
          <div class="p-5 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Gestionamos tus redes con estrategias personalizadas, contenido creativo y monitoreo constante para maximizar tu engagement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Script de Flowbite -->
<script src="https://unpkg.com/flowbite@1.8.1/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>